text: Joshua Schoenfeld (born 3 July 1997) is an Australian rules footballer playing for the Gold Coast Football Club in the Australian Football League (AFL). He was drafted by the Gold Coast Football Club with their third selection and thirty-fourth overall in the 2015 national draft. He made his debut in the twenty-four point win against in round 18, 2016 at Metricon Stadium. He kicked his first goal against the Brisbane Lions in Round 1 of the 2017 season. Schoenfeld was delisted by the Suns at the conclusion of the 2019 AFL season, but he was re-drafted in the 2019 Rookie Draft. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Gold Coast Football Club players Category:Peel Thunder Football Club players Category:Australian rules footballers from Western Australia
